OL,3,CArt competition shows the horror of
OL,4,Cwar through the eyes of children
OL,6,FThe competition, open to children in
OL,7,Fthe UK and across the world, was
OL,8,Flaunched by the Azerbaijani diaspora
OL,9,Fin the UK, to mark the 30th
OL,10,Fanniversary of the Khojaly massacre
OL,11,Fthat took place on the night of
OL,12,FFebruary 26, 1992, in Azerbaijan. 613
OL,13,Fcivilians, including 106 women and 63
OL,14,Fchildren were killed.
