OL,3,CArt competition shows the horror of
OL,4,Cwar through the eyes of children
OL,6,FNow, with the world so wracked by
OL,7,Fconflict, one of the organisers,
OL,8,FNarmina Mammadova, is appealing to
OL,9,Fchildren around the world to engage
OL,10,Fand encourage young people to consider
OL,11,Fthe reality of war and the importance
OL,12,Fof peace.
OL,14,FShe believes engaging through art and
OL,15,Fwriting helps children better
OL,16,Funderstand the realities faced by
OL,17,Ftheir counterparts in conflict zones
OL,18,Fand process their own emotions about
OL,19,Fthe state of the world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
