OL,3,CArt competition shows the horror of
OL,4,Cwar through the eyes of children
OL,6,F"The competition aims to nurture
OL,7,Fempathy, understanding, and a
OL,8,Fcommitment to peace, all while giving
OL,9,Fchildren a platform to express
OL,10,Fthemselves, "Mammadova said.
OL,12,F"I feel that the children of Khojaly,
OL,13,Fwho remained silent amidst the snowy
OL,14,Fhills, have not had their voices
OL,15,Fheard, and their deaths seem in vain.
OL,17,F"Through this competition, I want to
OL,18,Fremind the world that we must give a
OL,19,Fvoice to the children ` like those of
OL,20,FKhojaly ` who have endured
OL,21,Funimaginable suffering.
