OL,4,Cwar through the eyes of children
OL,6,F"While I cannot directly help those
OL,7,Flost children, I can tell their
OL,8,Fstories. It is our responsibility to
OL,9,Fensure their stories are heard."
OL,11,FArtwork from previous competitions has
OL,12,Fnow been featured in an exhibition by
OL,13,Fthe artist Arabella Dorman seeking to
OL,14,Fdepict the trauma of war on children
OL,15,Fin Ukraine.
OL,17,FThis competition also helps to raise
OL,18,Fmoney for charities such as War Child
OL,19,Fand Beyond Conflict, in order to
OL,20,Fcontinue their work in war zones
OL,21,Faround the world.
