OL,3,CArt competition shows the horror of
OL,4,Cwar through the eyes of children
OL,6,FThe collapse of the former Soviet
OL,7,FUnion brought with it a wave of
OL,8,Fbloodshed and conflicts that swept
OL,9,Facross many of its former republics,
OL,10,Fleaving a profound impact on every
OL,11,Faspect of life ` especially for the
OL,12,Finnocent children caught in the
OL,13,Fcrossfire.
OL,15,FAs a child, I witnessed firsthand the
OL,16,Fdevastating impact that conflict has
OL,17,Fon people, especially children and
OL,18,Fwomen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
