OL,6,FHowever, the memory that has stayed
OL,7,Fwith me the most is the Khojaly
OL,8,Fmassacre, a tragic event in Azerbaijan
OL,9,Fin 1992.
OL,11,FThe horror of that night, which
OL,12,Fclaimed the lives of 613 civilians `
OL,13,Fincluding 106 women, 63 children, and
OL,14,F70 elderly people ` still haunts me.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
