OL,3,CArt competition shows the horror of
OL,4,Cwar through the eyes of children
OL,6,FThe images from newspapers and news
OL,7,Freports are etched in my memory. I
OL,8,Fbecame friends with a young girl who
OL,9,Fhad become a refugee after losing her
OL,10,Fhome in Agdam, a town near Khojaly,
OL,11,Fwhich was called by journalists,
OL,12,F'Hiroshima of the Caucasus' for the
OL,13,Flevel of destruction it received
OL,14,Fduring the war in the 90s.
OL,16,FThat girl had to live with her aunt,
OL,17,Fwho was our neighbour in Baku.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
