OL,4,Cwar through the eyes of children
OL,6,FI remember her eyes, never laughed, so
OL,7,Fdeep pain that's impossible to
OL,8,Fdescribe. Our neighbour's two-bedroom
OL,9,Fapartment housed seven people, as the
OL,10,Ffamily of that girl, who had nowhere
OL,11,Felse to go, sought shelter there.
OL,13,FThe girl was only a year younger than
OL,14,Fme, and while her situation was
OL,15,Fdifficult, thousands of others weren't
OL,16,Feven that fortunate ` they lived in
OL,17,Ftents for years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
