OL,3,CArt competition shows the horror of
OL,4,Cwar through the eyes of children
OL,6,FThe sight of those refugee tents and
OL,7,Fthe pain and despair on the faces of
OL,8,Fthose living in them was a daily
OL,9,Freality for me, whether I was on my
OL,10,Fway to school or shopping. These
OL,11,Fmemories remain with me to this day.
OL,13,FIn 2022, on the 30th anniversary of
OL,14,Fthe Khojaly massacre, I had the chance
OL,15,Fto interview Afsana, one of the
OL,16,Fsurvivors.
OL,18,FHer story painted a heartbreaking
OL,19,Fpicture of the suffering her community
OL,20,Ffaced while trying to escape under
OL,21,Fsiege.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
