OL,4,Cwar through the eyes of children
OL,6,FThe imagery of children and families
OL,7,Ftrapped in the icy forests, falling
OL,8,Fvictim to relentless attacks, deeply
OL,9,Fmoved me.
OL,11,FThis encounter inspired me to create a
OL,12,Fplatform that could bridge the gap
OL,13,Fbetween children in peaceful countries
OL,14,Fand those affected by war, fostering
OL,15,Fempathy and understanding.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
